data.description: Extraordinary custom steel built home sits on 18.68 acres with panoramic mountain views. Walk into a open floor plan with tile flooring throughout, two living rooms, custom built in shelving, and custom kitchen with knotty cabinetry, electric stove range with gas hookup, and large pantry closet. Main suite with walk-in closet, garden tub and walk in shower. Spacious guest bedrooms and guest bathroom with roll-in handicap accessible shower. Sit out and enjoy the scenery in the covered patio or front porch. Spacious 2-car garage with shelving. Acreage is all useable land to add barns, horse corrals, and includes a 2nd septic tank for a 2nd home. A must see to appreciate the features this property has to offer.
